name: extreme_with_nested_bindings_if_roundtrip
section: binding-scope-deep
args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [x (if {cond} {a} {b})] (with [y (+ x {c})] (= (- y {c}) x)))
